{"tid":786261,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"小明在安全島，看見上司拖著一個印印","createTime":"2018-08-19T20:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T06:01:30.000Z","uid":43751,"like":665,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":133,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa242849ac0b7b0a595f5037cad05b67cbb49c5","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:08:14.000Z","msg":"安全島很小<br />\n人很多<br />\n小明縮在人群<br />\n希望沒被發覺<br />\n<br />\n發現一個秘技 可以發達<br />\n發現一個秘密 可能有殺生之禍<br />\n<br />\n小明窺看上司<br />\n上司甜蜜<br />\n是印傭 是印尼藉香港居民？小明問自己<br />\n小明沒有答案"},{"pid":"0d15a0ff96c1c3024e5649154d10305d71bd2840","tid":786261,"uid":27251,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:10:42.000Z","msg":"愛情話黎就黎"},{"pid":"74404d99c0bd2ea90a44563778f72df4b0920037","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":148,"dislike":2,"score":146,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:11:37.000Z","msg":"上司右手拖著一個印印<br />\n左右無名指有婚戒 有正印<br />\n<br />\n小明心跳得快 有點尷尬<br />\n紅燈成為綠燈<br />\n小明不知往那邊去<br />\n上司與印印走向北<br />\n小明惟有向南<br />\n<br />\n立下來<br />\n小明醒起應該過馬路<br />\n卻回到原地<br />\n活著 無可奈何"},{"pid":"10ed55aed20c4c4b0a6eae454f740b5c89726d9e","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:14:27.000Z","msg":"小明望著馬路<br />\n不見上司的影子<br />\n還是不敢過馬路<br />\n到七十一買了啤酒<br />\n飲了兩口壯膽子<br />\n<br />\n七十一有兩個鬼佬<br />\n小明跟鬼佬們對望兩眼<br />\n談起來<br />\n成為了朋友<br />\n一起在七十一飲酒<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬請小明飲威士忌<br />\n小明很醉<br />\n醉了 張開眼睛便在家中<br />\n小明自己的家"},{"pid":"f15f9ce27f32d0c713544ea446ff52735a5b2464","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":503,"dislike":3,"score":500,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:16:51.000Z","msg":"不知道是烈酒 抑或七月猛鬼<br />\n小明失去了昨天的記憶<br />\n<br />\n扭開電話<br />\n十點鐘<br />\n又遲到<br />\n小明心想：我酒量不應該如此差<br />\n<br />\n再看電話<br />\n昨晚發了一個短訊給上司：印印 印印 心心相印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28f1364bd41c2a34593ff13ab75db440cc7f2be","tid":786261,"uid":134729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:21:32.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c81c292878c82cef37378032b62f1ed8282e227f","tid":786261,"uid":5205,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:22:26.000Z","msg":"酒島吾酒?吾酒仙?"},{"pid":"2bbf416754ad53dfd8a5ac015b6b6a11a0cd3748","tid":786261,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243dad14115b97f75d3811b195334f74882087fc","tid":786261,"uid":77798,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"c81c292878c82cef37378032b62f1ed8282e227f","tid":786261,"uid":5205,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:22:26.000Z","msg":"酒島吾酒?吾酒仙?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:30:10.000Z","msg":"尷尬"},{"pid":"b461a74c79b4a955a757815eba0fc0d67b92a2c1","tid":786261,"uid":187850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:30:46.000Z","msg":"我準備好了"},{"pid":"44421a1b59dce184d11504173427468333af2bff","tid":786261,"uid":151048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T20:59:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1a4d3a322427a98851c0cb48ca9f3388d1922647","tid":786261,"uid":153518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T21:18:26.000Z","msg":"小明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d537f976fee837f4ad06e5c54e769b9edc8e29d","tid":786261,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T21:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea038c329db270268013838194b1ef159d7405c2","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T21:50:21.000Z","msg":"上司已讀不回"},{"pid":"567622bf8ad2f794d317d6a3aa9394fdc7c2a79b","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T21:55:50.000Z","msg":"留下一陣風 倒底誰能懂 這時的心情"},{"pid":"5d297a76036fc2bc3e2c30990b419ef73dff7d40","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T21:57:21.000Z","msg":"上司很明白 小明看見自己拖著印印<br />\n但小明沒有看見自己戴一頂綠帽<br />\n綠帽 看不見的綠帽 是不是綠色？"},{"pid":"90d978b18d6b5ba47f1be6dbad59f6980f77354e","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:03:27.000Z","msg":"上司的老婆給上司戴了一頂綠帽<br />\n上司以為自己會憤怒<br />\n但沒有<br />\n<br />\n上司的樓 是岳父給首期<br />\n上司已經往慣了有空間的房子<br />\n幻想不到 要搬出去的生活<br />\n一切都習慣了<br />\n太懶惰"},{"pid":"cc667dc42edcc68b342075fd71b650530304f92e","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:07:12.000Z","msg":"兒子只有三歲<br />\n上司不希望兒子分對錯<br />\n&ldquo;我對 你媽錯&rdquo;<br />\n上司覺得這說話 對小童 有不良發展"},{"pid":"c12fda6e2da96243eb20f72f72b9f9f99e3fe8fe","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:08:37.000Z","msg":"上司不希望離婚 然後把通姦證據 放上法庭<br />\n向老婆拿贍養費<br />\n<br />\n上司賺的錢比老婆少"},{"pid":"cf66cddc0a852c346a361ce00f29ee7e4bedec34","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:14:22.000Z","msg":"上司只想生存<br />\n無風無浪<br />\n<br />\n受想行識 亦復如是"},{"pid":"765341c8f659ddf771917e81212fb46a8bd5c6af","tid":786261,"uid":53774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:16:08.000Z","msg":"俾雷劈"},{"pid":"2f3bf4350466f79f8dd087da8a3277da9330868e","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":160,"dislike":1,"score":159,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:16:56.000Z","msg":"上司慢慢發覺 戴綠帽也不錯<br />\n起碼責任不在自己<br />\n(當然有些傻西會把責任放在自己身上)<br />\n<br />\n起碼到上帝審判人類的未日<br />\n上司也能上天堂<br />\n畢竟 戴綠帽 沒有被梵蒂岡禁止"},{"pid":"0f260b7eca49eb74bd1abb0dddef987c12978125","tid":786261,"uid":44704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e64100b7cc3c235ad61462dc6cdb8692ef7d9fb","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":161,"dislike":0,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:23:17.000Z","msg":"與其說 發現老婆偷情是戴綠帽<br />\n上司覺得是戴眼鏡<br />\n<br />\n看清一切都虛假<br />\n而上司選擇 在虛假的世界 做一個虛假的角色<br />\n懦弱<br />\n<br />\n但上司發覺 抽身出去<br />\n反而自在 瀟灑<br />\n<br />\n做一個活生生的人 必然率直<br />\n做一個角色 卻可以使用不少技巧"},{"pid":"b2f932b2635b3c2b567ab002cb31025efa60f34b","tid":786261,"uid":104000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8810783b840941bcf59b551a06c46652242d40","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:28:16.000Z","msg":"韓國有人被強奸<br />\n菲國有人坐冤獄<br />\n<br />\n上司買了一扎花 給老婆<br />\n不是生日節日<br />\n純粹想做個浪漫的丈夫<br />\n上司心想：老婆會內疚或討厭嗎？<br />\n上司沒有想太多<br />\n上司只是做一個角色<br />\n好老公的角色"},{"pid":"afa95fe6c7eb0d02cb55031f20069f78d1096a48","tid":786261,"uid":67931,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:32:23.000Z","msg":"扮演太投入，分不清做人或是做角色了"},{"pid":"879ed5a88333d2ace7da6d036e0f1178f33b4958","tid":786261,"uid":33190,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:32:27.000Z","msg":"呢篇野不得了"},{"pid":"b972bd24805d54053d2f58008ddea845ceea4cd7","tid":786261,"uid":27151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:33:40.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇過小明出新故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcd300374f310767c66afa77728680d9dcb3bb9","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":183,"dislike":2,"score":181,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:39:34.000Z","msg":"上司在地鐵<br />\n故意叫一個坐關愛座的廢青讓座給廢老<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;不好意思 能讓一讓給我爸爸嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n然後遞了一張五十元紙給廢青<br />\n廢青不好意思接 推開上司的手<br />\n<br />\n上司說了一聲感謝<br />\n廢老像哈巴狗一樣 稱讚上司 也稱讚廢青<br />\n<br />\n廢老不是上司的爸爸<br />\n上司純粹想廢青讓座<br />\n然後拿到光環<br />\n<br />\n上司覺得<br />\n在矯枉過正的世界 活得更矯枉過正 <br />\n有樂趣<br />\n<br />\n前提是 要送禮<br />\n世界上的人 面對禮 都軟弱無力"},{"pid":"9c1f95462ecdc6c5c1001e12f2163a39f18affff","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:48:14.000Z","msg":"有些人會為感情問題 而自殺<br />\n上司喜歡 達爾文<br />\n物應天擇 適者生存<br />\n要生存 就得適應<br />\n能適應 就能夠進化"},{"pid":"829052f175a67a92e65412a867c78655a012b8d4","tid":786261,"uid":38648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:51:24.000Z","msg":"小明真係屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b8f7a0a09484bde32aaac201106ba054217aa5","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":178,"dislike":2,"score":176,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:55:58.000Z","msg":"有些馬騮成了人 有些卻留在籠或森林<br />\n<br />\n因為某些馬騮開始不想做馬騮 才進化成人的<br />\n<br />\n每隻馬騮不介意奪取領導 賣命<br />\n人 卻不介意一直做奴隸<br />\n<br />\n人們在看籠中的領袖<br />\n馬騮們在看籠外的奴隸<br />\n<br />\n悉隨專便"},{"pid":"b74fafa82cff52dcf93e343f88713a22f9faa207","tid":786261,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf66cddc0a852c346a361ce00f29ee7e4bedec34","tid":786261,"uid":43751,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:14:22.000Z","msg":"上司只想生存<br />\n無風無浪<br />\n<br />\n受想行識 亦復如是"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T22:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d488aa1d09bfa0927f9d3dde8cd604bf6a436f79","tid":786261,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T23:08:37.000Z","msg":"馬騮比人更幸福吧<br />\n至少打輸亦無憾"},{"pid":"f284a18bc68846119139a9fde73c7524061eb391","tid":786261,"uid":4303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T23:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8c3dd58910e51518478855a476200b4b2c290f","tid":786261,"uid":33174,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:32:10.000Z","msg":"新一代傷痕文學"},{"pid":"e5f624764d367